attributes.name: Jack Herer | ORALE
attributes.body: Jack Herer, also known as "JH," "The Jack," "Premium Jack," and "Platinum Jack" is a sativa-dominant marijuana strain that has gained as much renown as its namesake, the marijuana activist and author of The Emperor Wears No Clothes. Combining a Haze hybrid with a Northern Lights #5 and Shiva Skunk cross, Sensi Seeds created Jack Herer hoping to capture both cerebral elevation and heavy resin production. Its rich genetic background gives rise to several different variations of Jack Herer, each phenotype bearing its own unique features and effects. Leafly reviewers tell us that Jack Herer’s effects include feeling energetic, creative, and uplifted. However, consumers typically describe this 55% sativa hybrid as blissful, clear-headed, and creative. Jack Herer was created in the Netherlands in the mid-1990s, where it was later distributed by Dutch pharmacies as a recognized medical-grade strain. Since then, this spicy, pine-scented strain has taken home numerous awards for its quality and potency. Orale! ORALE vape carts and disposables are distilled 3 times to create a refined distillate that is void of all impurities and has maximum THC potency levels to elevate your enchantment and pure satisfaction. ORALE distillate has only two ingredients - cannabinoids and terpenes. We don't believe in using any artificial ingredients. As health conscious cannabis enthusiasts we strive to create carts and vapes right here in New Mexico that make you feel as good as they taste. Our formulas are backed by years of research and design and customer feedback We use top of the line hardware for our vape carts to ensure you have a smooth and flavorful experience from first puff to last. When it comes to carts and disposable vapes, we ORALE always delvers!

attributes.name: AiroPod - GSC - Hybrid - .5g
attributes.body:
AiroPod Strain Series .5g Cartridge

• Strain Series

• Hybrid

• GSC

• Pure Distillate Oil

• Full Terpene Profile

• High Potency

 

The AiroPod cartridge is more than a stylish magnet, it’s the first vessel of its kind. The secured mouthpiece and filling septum minimize the possibility of leakage, something which has been a common issue among older model vaporizers. Considering that risk of accidental exposure, to children or pets for example, the AiroPod cartridge was built for safety as well as durability.

Free from a traditional wick and coil setup, AiroPod cartridges adopted ceramic reactor technology to serve as the heating element. Unmatched thermal precision ensures concentrates are always vaporized at the proper temperature. This preserves the flavor of concentrates and prevents them from burning. The silver-plated magnetic base makes exchanging cartridges a snap, while ensuring a solid connection every time.

attributes.body: Embrace and empower your day with the Pineapple Diesel. Pineapple Diesel is a sativa-dominant, cross of Hybrid Pineapple and Sativa Sour Diesel. Inhale to clear your mind and grab the reins of your day. Taste the earthy, peppery, and lemony terpenes of Caryophyllene, Limonene, and Myrcene. As you exhale, feel full-body stimulation with motivating cerebral effects that will prepare you for any activity.

Arouse your palate with vapor full of colorful fruit, floral, and savory notes. Our Story Airo Brands is driven to create an intuitive, virtually effortless, and cleverly designed vapor experience. Our team saw what the vape world had to offer, and we knew we could do it better with a focus on design, vapor delivery, quality, and one-of-a-kind oils. We organically formed a working belief that drives us each day: no detail too small. **AiroPod Cartridges are only compatible with the AiroPro and AiroSport Vaporizer.**

Exhale the sunshine to brighten your day, awaken your senses, and saturate the room with freshly squeezed orange aromas. This Sativa reveals your aurora so it illuminates throughout your day. attributes.name: Forbidden Cake | Outdoor
attributes.body: Cross between Wedding Cake x Forbidden Fruit In 2015 we were shovel ready and applied but were denied licensure due to political shenanigans in Santa Fe. Unwilling to accept defeat or wait years to start this journey we are grateful that one badass company known as Urban Wellness with great forward thinking leaders gave us a chance to prove our concepts and build a track record of success working under their license. That lasted from 2016 though 2021 when we were awarded the first production license following the passage of the Cannabis Regulation Act. Getting our own license allowed us to scale our systems and grow our community. Today we work with 15 groups of contractors/people that make up the #LavaLeafCollective or #FarmFamily working on our property. We have also helped 4 family owned companies with similar values to obtain licensure and to get their cultivation operations off the ground. One major differentiator that we hope becomes the norm, is that we do not hire growers we partner with them. We believe that business owners will take more pride in and responsibility for their work. This means that more love and care is given to each nugget of flower Lava Leaf produces. New Mexico is home to many great producers so high quality is now par for the course. Now we are leveling up our systems and driving a conversation around equity and the sustainability of cannabis production. When purchasing cannabis we hope people will question, how was this grown? Was it a sustainable use of water and power? Does this company recycle? Are the growers or creators of this product valued?

attributes.name: RSO | Syringe
attributes.body: What is RSO? Put simply, RSO is an oil derived from cannabis. But rather than a solvent extract that strips trichomes from buds, RSO contains all the cannabinoids, terpenes, and additional compounds of the whole cannabis plant. The extraction process is complex and fairly long, similar to making a tincture. It’s typically near-black in color, and, admittedly, doesn’t taste great due to its high amount of plant matter (it uses the whole plant). RSO was created as a medicinal therapeutic for cancer and other chronic health conditions, like MS and asthma. While Rick Simpson no longer produces the oil himself, it remains a crucial ingredient in the treatment plans of patients across North America.

attributes.body: Unlike other cherry gummies on the market which taste like cough syrup, our cherry gummies are perfectly balanced with the right amount of authentic cherry flavor, complimented by bright lime flavor before being rolled in our sourest sugar.

attributes.name: Golden Poppy
attributes.body: Prohibition 37 flower is our specialty and what we have built our brand on. Our production facilities include 2 state-of-the-art indoor cultivations totaling 14,000 sq ft in our home city of Albuquerque. We also have an outdoor farm in Belen, and greenhouse productions in Belen and Gallup. Our mission is to destigmatize the industry, produce outstanding quality cannabis, and positively contribute to the quality of life of our patients and customers. We currently grow over 75 cultivars, and are continually adding the newest and most sought after genetics to bring to every corner of New Mexico. WHO IS P37? Prohibition 37 is a physician-led, nationally recognized, and award-winning vertical cannabis company. P37 is highly focused on the customer experience and science of the medicinal and recreational effects of its many products. Our name is derived from The Marihuana Tax Act of 1937, which was a U.S. federal law that effectively criminalized the possession and distribution of marijuana. While it did not directly ban the cannabis plant, it imposed strict regulations and heavy taxes on its cultivation, sales, and use. This made it impossible to legally engage in these activities, leading to a de facto prohibition of cannabis. The Act played a significant role in shaping the modern approach to marijuana regulation in the United States.\ SOCIAL EQUITY AND JUSTICE The Marihuana Tax Act of 1937 disproportionately targeted minorities, particularly African, Mexican, and Jewish American communities. While the act did not explicitly mention racial or ethnic groups, its implementation and enforcement were marked by tremendous racial bias and discrimination. Law enforcement, for example, selectively targeted and arrested individuals from minority groups and used marijuana-related offenses as a pretext for discriminatory actions. This contributed to the disproportionate impact of the Act on minorities, perpetuating racial stereotypes and injustices for generations to come. Our mission at Prohibition 37 is to reverse decades of cannabis-related injustice and create a healthy, communal, and scientific approach to cannabis use.

attributes.name: Fruity Pebbles | Distillate Cart
attributes.body: CONTROLLED EXTRACTIONREMEDIATIONDISTILLATION We achieve Molecular Perfection within our Premium Distillate products via methodologies found commonly in other industries. Much like filtered water, cooking oils and other natural plant oil products, refinement is used to isolate specific desired compounds found with the different organic starting materials. Cannabis is a complex organic plant material that contains compounds which are not considered “healthy” for ingestion or inhalation via vaporization. The predominant compounds within cannabis that interest us are called “Cannabinoids”. A plethora of data and litereture suggest that cannabinoids are beneficial to many aspects of human health. Through refinement and isolation we can offer consumers a clean way to enjoy cannabinoids without plant volatiles, waxes and fats found in pre-processed cannabis biomass materials or crude extracts. At Pharmers, we employ methods of modern chemistry to refine crude cannabis extract into a pure, cannabinoid rich, odorless, and tasteless distillate oil. Demonstrated through decades of experience in extracting and refining, our founder Don Romero, properly named “The Distillate Don”, became a trusted source of education and consultation for industry giants from coast to coast. With Don at the helm, Pharmers Quality has established itself nationally as the expert level extraction and distillation specialists. What makes our oil different? It’s simple, purity through proper processes. When enjoying Pharmers, the consumer can trust they have a safe, clean, and pure product in their hands.

attributes.name: Red Chili Tophee
attributes.body: As Pharmers Inphusions delve into history, they bring a fresh new flavor to a classic treat. Whether it’s nostalgia or exploration, our unique blend of local and traditional ingredients will tickle your taste buds. Featuring the highest quality D9-THC distillates, it is sure to produce a quality high!

attributes.name: Dream Berry | Fast Asleep Gummies
attributes.body: Feel sleepy in just 5-15 minutes... with no next-day grogginess. These revolutionary nighttime gummies deliver a sweet mixed berry flavor, along with a custom blend of CBD, THC, CBG, CBN, and melatonin. They’re also enhanced with more than 30 specialized terpenes, curated based on AI-generated data from thousands of consumer experiences — and all delivered via fast-acting molecular encapsulation technology. What Makes Us Wana? Excellence. We've never been satisfied with "good enough," not even when we were just a scrappy Boulder-based start-up trying to make our way in a newly legalized industry. When many companies cut corners, using inferior ingredients like animal-derived gelatin and artificial sweeteners, we crafted a vegan, terpene-enhanced, melt-proof recipe that virtually any adult could enjoy. While our competitors waited for state regulations to require testing, we tested our products for potency and consistency from the start. And now, more than a decade later, customers all over the U.S. and Canada trust us to deliver a premium cannabis experience, every time they reach for a Wana product.

attributes.name: Skywalker | Surf Disposable
attributes.body: A new kind of force. Send stress to a galaxy far, far away with this relaxing indica. B-Myrcene: Naturally Found In: mango, wild thyme, cardamom, hops Valencene: Naturally Found In: Valencia oranges Linalool: Naturally Found In: lavender, cilantro, basil.

attributes.name: Ghost Train Haze 2g All-In-One Vape
attributes.body: Ghost Train Haze is a potent sativa-dominant strain known for its high THC content. It often has a citrusy aroma with hints of floral and spice. Ghost Train Haze produces a strong cerebral high, characterized by intense euphoria, creativity, and an uplifting, energizing effect.

attributes.name: Enchanted Botanicals - Concord Cream
attributes.body: Concord Cream, a predominantly Indica strain, is the sweet sweet love child of Grape Bubba and Cookies & Cream. This soothing bud, rich in flavor, is a must-try for any grape strain fans. True to its name, Concord Cream boasts a super sweet and creamy fruity grape flavor complemented by notes of flowery violet and vanilla. The aroma mirrors this profile with a hint of sour grapefruit. Concord Cream is a favored choice for addressing various conditions across a whole spectrum, including stress, anxiety, muscle spasms, cramps, depression, and insomnia. The Concord Cream high unfolds gradually, initiating with a slow burn of euphoria that melts the mad/sad away. Concord Cream is wonderful for consumers that have social anxiety as its a very talkative, giggly strain! As the mental boost persists, a sense of physical relaxation takes over, eventually inducing a sleepy, sedative state.

attributes.name: Enchanted Botanicals - Lemon Skunk
attributes.body: Lemon Skunk is a Sativa Strain with a citrusy/skunky "Punch You In The Face" aroma and balanced effects. Lemon Skunk has dense, trichome-covered buds with vibrant green and orange hues with a higher than average THC content. Lemon Skunk is effective for people with Depression, Stress, and Nausea, with none of the energy that comes from your usual sativa.

attributes.name: Enchanted Botanicals - Modified Grapes
attributes.body: Modified Grapes is an Indica weed strain resulting from a cross between GMO and Purple Punch. This strain is favored by experienced cannabis consumers for its beautiful purple color and its flavors reminiscent of grape, berry, and honey. According to our customers, Modified Grapes is associated with effects like drowsiness, relaxation, and arousal. Consumers often turn to Modified Grapes to alleviate symptoms related to anxiety, stress, and insomnia.
